パッケージ ca.ciccc.java.model

クラス Model

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.ciccc.java.model.Model

  • public class Model
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represent person who is modeling. And, it is capable to calculate salary (pay per hour).
    It has attributes below.
    • firstName
    • lastName
    • height (Unit : inches)
    • weight (Unit : pounds)
    • canTravel
    • smokes
    • occupation [static]
    導入されたバージョン:
    2018-03-20
    作成者:
    shouhei.mizuno
